{
  "stem": "25912.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I have a memory of an 18-year-old brother, whom I never saw as a man.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once we were in Italy, there was a question of, what was I going to do?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- I needed to go to school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a school for families in the south of Italy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But having had me for such a short time, Father really didn't want me to go away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So somehow, he arranged that by falsifying my date of birth and my age, I could join the army.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The problem was that, although the powers to be knew that I was younger, nobody told the medical commission that I was 15 and not 18.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The result was that I got category-- medical category C, and was rejected as being underdeveloped-- [LAUGHS] for age 18.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So subsequently, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was granted special permission by General Anders, the commander of the Polish Second Corps, to be accepted into the army despite my category C.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And thereby, I was able to go to a secondary school for eight years, which was located only a short distance from where my father was.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was located in Porto San Giorgio.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I met there a number of my friends from the Girl Guides in Warsaw, who knew when I was younger, but that didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I must say that during a period, '39-'45, my education was sketchy, to say the least.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had periods when I had some lessons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had periods when I didn't have any.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I learned a little bit of Latin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I learned a little bit of maths, history because I was reading books.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was quite well read in literature.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
